=============================================================================

Fix in this version:
- Final reduce step no longer crashes if it returns empty.
- It retries with smaller combined text and if still empty, falls back to a stitched summary.

Outputs:
- DOCX + HTML + (optional) PDF + stats JSON + failures log

Requirements:
- OPENAI_API_KEY set in env (already in your notebook)
- extract-msg installed for .msg parsing (recommended)
- python-docx installed for docx output
- reportlab optional for PDF output
"""

